            "description": "Delete a video and **all** its files from MinIO (raw upload + processed HLS segments + thumbnail).\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Video deleted\",\n  \"videoId\": \"uuid-here\"\n}\n```"
